    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push, combine, and deliver pastries with the help of your hats in Hat Helpers, a cozy 3D grid-based puzzle game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256070/extras/38dfccabe53935ced967e9d144b178b0.poster.avif?t=1738240323\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256070/extras/38dfccabe53935ced967e9d144b178b0.webm?t=1738240323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256070/extras/38dfccabe53935ced967e9d144b178b0.mp4?t=1738240323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles centered around one simple mechanic pushed to its limits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every puzzle is unique and teaches you something new</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interesting solutions with a focus on &quot;Aha!&quot; moments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Made one wrong move? Don't worry! Just press Z to undo any mistake</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No distractions, just fun puzzles!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256070/extras/12d5b5aa02276dedd5c7db24cca0b6c2.poster.avif?t=1738240323\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256070/extras/12d5b5aa02276dedd5c7db24cca0b6c2.webm?t=1738240323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256070/extras/12d5b5aa02276dedd5c7db24cca0b6c2.mp4?t=1738240323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Embark on a grand puzzle journey with your hat helpers over several different worlds. Each<br>with a unique aesthetic and puzzles which build upon what you have learned.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256070/extras/124d91aa1e4c77710f33691bf4dc3c2d.poster.avif?t=1738240323\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256070/extras/124d91aa1e4c77710f33691bf4dc3c2d.webm?t=1738240323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256070/extras/124d91aa1e4c77710f33691bf4dc3c2d.mp4?t=1738240323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
